/>\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67739e9b6a47c0a79d8ec2ec08a3734dbc3db743","tid":1544821,"uid":203507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4241acdc22084d2c451a050abfc8cba114b73fd8","tid":1544821,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"平機票400-500都應該有?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31598355972f67d1b417f1e64db246e6d21a4eb7","tid":1544821,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67739e9b6a47c0a79d8ec2ec08a3734dbc3db743","tid":1544821,"uid":203507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4241acdc22084d2c451a050abfc8cba114b73fd8","tid":1544821,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"平機票400-500都應該有?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"我求其用scoot search星期六新加坡 $700"},{"pid":"09bd95ab658ec4e638a6a6a0c013881fbc726f96","tid":1544821,"uid":208644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54fbf16ec94c2b957d94df1e8b41104892bd7941","tid":1544821,"uid":208644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ba7e1d8d3cb3ca084a6e03bbdaab88b01c52a7d","tid":1544821,"uid":208644,"like